axing our assumption of a fixed planetesimal disk.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Jan 2007 21:10:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 28 Jan 2007 20:33:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
